'''Farta Boorama''' ({{lang-en|Borama alphabet}}; Qaabka qoraalka: [[File:Boorama.jpg|60px]]) (sidoo kale loo yaqaano: '''Far Gadabuursi''') waa nidaam [[qoraal|wax-qoris]] oo ka mid ah [[Far Soomaali]]ga taasi oo uu alifey [[Sheekh Cabdiraxmaan Sheekh Nuur]]. Sida taariikhda lagu hayo, Sheekh Cabdiraxmaan wuxuu alifey fartan sanadkii 1933 wakhtigaasi oo uu ku sugnaa magaalada [[Boorama]], oo noqonaysa sababta farta loogu magacdaray magaaladaasi.<ref>{{cite book|author=David D. Laitin|title=Politics, Language, and Thought: The Somali Experience|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=LR8A4tEYZUAC&pg=PA98|accessdate=2 July 2012|date=1 May 1977|publisher=University of Chicago Press|isbn=978-0-226-46791-7|pages=98–}}</ref>

